flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic (daily) data refresh from SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest KPI data from SAP S/4HANA]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze KPI data using Cortex Auto Forecast]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Perform cost-to-serve analysis using AutoML]
  N3 --> N4[Stream: STREAMS - Monitor SLA adherence using STREAMS]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: RCA Service - Identify logistics bottlenecks using RCA Service]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Execute automated workflows for optimization]
  N6 --> N7{Decision: Automate decisions for inventory positioning, safety stock, production/line sequencing, and dynamic fulfillment routing to reduce COGS and improve OTIF.}
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved order fulfillment metrics, and enhanced overall logistics network performance.]
  N7 -->|SLA breach detected| B1[Trigger remediation workflow]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: SLA adherence restored.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|High-cost-to-serve identified| B2[Initiate cost reduction measures]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Total logistics cost reduced.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Bottleneck identified| B3[Develop and execute mitigation plan]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Network throughput improved.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]